@startuml runtime

skinparam defaultFontName Liberation Sans
skinparam defaultFontSize 10
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign left

skinparam participant {
  BorderColor #0056A0
  BackgroundColor #D6E8F7
  FontColor #003087
  FontStyle bold
}

skinparam actor {
  BorderColor #8B4513
  BackgroundColor #F5E6D3
  FontColor #8B4513
  FontStyle bold
}

skinparam database {
  BorderColor #5a7a3a
  BackgroundColor #E6F0D8
  FontColor #3a5a1a
}

skinparam arrow {
  Color #333333
  FontColor #444444
}

skinparam note {
  BorderColor #aaaaaa
  BackgroundColor #FFFDE7
  FontSize 9
}

actor       "User"         as user
participant "Frontend"     as frontend
participant "Controller"   as ctrl
participant "Service"      as svc
participant "Repository"   as repo
database    "PostgreSQL"   as db

user     ->  frontend  : 1. Submit simulation form
frontend ->  ctrl      : 2. POST /v1/simulations\n   (JSON body + Bearer token)

note over ctrl
  3. Validate JWT
     Parse SimulationCreate schema
end note

ctrl     ->  svc       : 4. service.run(data, user_id)
svc      ->  repo      : 5. matrix_repo.get_by_id(matrix_id)
repo     ->  db        : 6. SELECT population_matrices
db       --> repo      : 7. ORM row
repo     --> svc       : 8. PopulationMatrix object

note over svc
  9. A @ v loop — NumPy
     (CPU-only, no I/O)
end note

svc      ->  repo      : 10. sim_repo.create(...)
repo     ->  db        : 11. INSERT simulation_runs
db       --> repo      : 12. SimulationRun row
repo     --> svc       : 13. ORM object
svc      --> ctrl      : 14. SimulationRecord (Pydantic)
ctrl     --> frontend  : 15. HTTP 201 JSON
frontend --> user      : 16. Render population dynamics plot

@enduml
